    "Challenges in Information Retrieval AccuracyThe accuracy of information retrieval in LLMs has been a persistent challenge.",
    "Initial issues centered around the models?",
    "tendency to replicate biases present in their training data, leading to skewed or discriminatory responses [4,5].",
    "Another significant challenge was the handling of factually incorrect information, where LLMs often confidently presented erroneous data as accurate [27,28].",
    "The dynamic nature of information posed a problem, with models struggling to update their knowledge base in line with real-world changes [29]."
